snippet.title: inZOI @ gamescom ONL Pre-show 2024
snippet.description:
Yesterday, inZOI made its debut during the Opening Night Live Pre-show at #gamescom 🎮

The video turned out to be something truly special, and we can’t wait for you to experience it. If you haven’t watched it yet, be sure to check it out! 👀

#inZOI #KRAFTON #LifeSimulation
#gamescom #gamescom2024 #gamescomONL
